9 ODEM DUTIES
10
11 SECTION 8. ORS 401.114 is amended to read:
12 401.114. The Oregon Department of Emergency Management shall carry out the following func-
13 tions:
14 (1) Coordinate emergency management functions on a regional basis within this state;
15 (2) Coordinate training related to emergency response on a regional basis within this state;
16 [and]
17 (3) Develop and carry out emergency preparedness exercises on a statewide basis[.];
18 (4) Oversee collaboration, cooperation and coordination between the state and organiza-
19 tions involved in the emergency stockpile plan described in ORS 401.111, the emergency
20 preparedness equipment grant program described in ORS 401.551 and other stockpile or
21 emergency preparedness programs carried out by state agencies;
22 (5) Take actions as necessary to ensure that supplies, equipment and other materials are
23 appropriately staged in preparation for emergencies; and
24 (6) Develop and maintain an inventory plan for the sustainable procurement, rotation and
25 management of emergency preparedness assets.
